Quote: The "cargon", a New Zealand inventionused by Straits Air Freight Company tospeed the loading and unloading of itsair freighters at Paraparaumu, may beadopted for use at most of the world'sairports in a few years' time... A bigcontainer, the "cargon" can be loaded inWellington and taken to Paraparaumu readyto put straight into the air freighters.
